She looked at Scorponok. She tilted her head and wondered if she was 
starting to like him. A program surge reminded her that her number one 
superior officer was standing right there and she needed orders from him 
only while he was around her. Her programming commanded her to obey Megatron 
first, Quickstrike second and Scorponok third. She walked over and looked at 
Megatron.

"Commander, what would you like us to move in first?  The power supply 
generators and get the lighting up?  Or start with the CR chamber  just in 
case?  I await your orders Megatron."
She stood infront of Megatron lowered her head to him as a sigh of 
submission and waited for him to give her his commands.
